cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper deals with multi-label image classification using deep ConvNets, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new loss function for learning with partial labels, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments are performed on large-scale datasets, which could also fall under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
